text: Hey Erin! Wow, sorry for the super late response, the holidays were nuts and I didn't see your message! I'm currently helping out on an indie film which has been an awesome way to learn since my supervisor is a comp artist full time. Definitely learned a lot about paint work and grain management.
I've also got a few ideas for new reel projects to work on that I'd like to run by you whenever you have a moment! As well as get some pointers for touching up some driving greenscreens I have.
